{"tid":1752034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔捨得麥美娟(娟娟)","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:46:42.000Z","uid":201669,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0c4e81e2104c98be5bbb78f0bfd0db0f6634de","tid":1752034,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"娟娟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「X街」<br />\n「你唔知呀，X你老X個女仔呀，X呀林鄭呀...只係你呢個女人識喊呀？我喊咗成晚！」<br />\n據《東周刊》報道，麥美娟當日在會議中大聲説：「你太天真啦！依家就算暫緩（修例）人哋都唔會收貨！」，又稱「唔好賴解説工作，一開始特區政府就低估政治形勢，我啲兄弟落去解説日日被人X！X街，你試下落區日日畀人X呀！」林鄭一臉錯愕，但繼續努力辯解。<br />\n麥美娟谷爆繼續狂數，話一味叫建制派唔好動搖，所以即使有逾百萬人遊行反修例，工聯會依然去美國領事館拉橫額鬧美國佬，麥繼續說「依家話撤就撤，咁當初有過百萬人上街，嗰時又憑咩咁堅定？」麥美娟鬧足5分鐘收唔到制，林鄭忍到呢一刻終於淚灑人前，麥美娟隨即說「依家喊有咩用？你識喊！我都識喊！」自己亦喊了出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49904d8aa7ea0c45fe8a005f195fdba000a5e6be","tid":1752034,"uid":202876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"嫁唔出係有理由的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8733ce21a8c8fd9147af870cbbc6d8ca8a80eec7","tid":1752034,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:48:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f74502b9dc96a5b6a3663bd33b167377dbe2fc9","tid":1752034,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c6c524dfe5a202413a9868387c9cb138ef08ec","tid":1752034,"uid":201